{"product_id":"organic-night-cream-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eRich organic night cream to intensely hydrate and nourish the skin overnight and stimulate skin regeneration.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), rosehip seed oil (soothing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), wheat germ oil (protecting) and organic extracts of chamomile (antiseptic), arnica (anti-inflammatory) and mallow (protecting).\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into freshly cleansed skin and neck. Use it in the evening and whenever your skin needs rich hydration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Glycerin**, Cera Alba**, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate*, Aqua*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Sorbitan Sesquioleate*, Oenothera Biennis Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Polyglyceryl-3 Ricinoleate, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Citric Acid*, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Viola Tricolor Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Geraniol**\/***, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,3%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** certified organic (89,2%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49093459968327,"sku":null,"price":59.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-night-cream-50ml-212703.jpg?v=1739897344","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/organic-night-cream-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}